## How to create a box

### VirtualBox

From the terminal, invoke the following command for VirtualBox provider:

    packer build -only=virtualbox-iso -var-file=vars-alpine-standard-3.12-x86_64.json alpine-3.12-minimal.json

You will find a vagrant box file named `Alpine-standard-3.12-x86_64-minimal-v12.3.20201216-virtualbox.box`
in the same directory after the command has succeeded.

Then you can add the box named `Alpine-standard-3.12-x86_64-minimal-v12.3.20201216`
to your box list by the following command:

    vagrant box add Alpine-standard-3.12-x86_64-minimal-v12.3.20201216-virtualbox.box --name Alpine-standard-3.12-x86_64-minimal-v12.3.20201216 --provider virtualbox

